---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Cascadas de Chile — Descubre las Caídas de Agua de Chile"
  description="Portal de las cascadas más impresionantes de Chile. Descubre saltos, cataratas y caídas de agua a lo largo de todo el país."
>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
       HERO
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section style="
    min-height: 100vh;
    background: #091d2b;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.6fr;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 0 2.5rem;
    padding-top: 64px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  ">
    <div style="
      position:absolute; inset:0; z-index:0; pointer-events:none;
      background-image: url('data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22 width=%22200%22 height=%22200%22><filter id=%22n%22><feTurbulence type=%22fractalNoise%22 baseFrequency=%220.65%22 numOctaves=%223%22 stitchTiles=%22stitch%22/><feColorMatrix type=%22saturate%22 values=%220%22/></filter><rect width=%22200%22 height=%22200%22 filter=%22url(%23n)%22 opacity=%220.03%22/></svg>');
    "></div>

    <div style="position:relative; z-index:1; display:flex; flex-direction:column; justify-content:space-between; height:70vh; padding: 4rem 0;">
      <div>
        <p style="
          color:#00e5d4; font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:500;
          letter-spacing:0.15em; text-transform:uppercase; margin:0 0 1.5rem;
        ">Portal de Cascadas</p>
        <p class="reveal" style="
          color:#f4efe6; font-size:clamp(1rem, 1.8vw, 1.35rem);
          line-height:1.55; max-width:360px; margin:0; font-weight:300;
        ">
          El directorio más completo de cascadas, saltos y caídas de agua a lo largo de toda Chile.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <a href="#cascadas" style="
          display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:0.5rem;
          color:#f4efe6; text-decoration:none; font-size:0.78rem;
          font-weight:500; letter-spacing:0.2em; text-transform:uppercase;
          opacity:0.7; transition:opacity 0.2s;
        ">
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none">
            <path d="M8 2v12M3 9l5 5 5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
          Descubrir
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div style="position:relative; z-index:1; text-align:right; line-height:0.88;">
      <h1 style="
        font-family:'Archivo Black',sans-serif;
        font-size: clamp(7rem, 15vw, 18rem);
        color: #00e5d4;
        margin: 0;
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        line-height: 0.88;
      ">
        CAER<br/>LIBRE
      </h1>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
       SPLIT — imagen + bloque de color
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; min-height:55vh;">
    <div style="
      background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1506905925346-21bda4d32df4?w=900&q=80');
      background-size: cover; background-position: center;
    "></div>
    <div style="
      background:#b8e8e4;
      display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
      padding:3rem;
    ">
      <div class="reveal">
        <p style="
          font-family:'Archivo Black',sans-serif;
          font-size:clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 5rem);
          color:#091d2b; margin:0; line-height:1;
          text-transform:uppercase;
        ">+500<br/>cascadas<br/>catalogadas</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
       MANIFIESTO — fondo crema, texto enorme centrado
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section id="sobre" style="
    background:#f4efe6;
    padding: 8rem 2.5rem;
    text-align:center;
  ">
    <h2 class="reveal" style="
      font-family:'Archivo Black',sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(5rem, 13vw, 16rem);
      color:#091d2b;
      margin:0; line-height:0.9;
      text-transform:uppercase;
      letter-spacing:-0.02em;
    ">
      CHILE<br/>SALVAJE
    </h2>
    <p class="reveal" style="
      max-width:600px; margin:4rem auto 0;
      font-size:clamp(1rem, 1.6vw, 1.25rem);
      color:#091d2b; line-height:1.65; font-weight:300;
    ">
      Desde la árida Atacama hasta los fiordos de Magallanes, Chile alberga
      algunas de las cascadas más espectaculares del mundo. Este portal nació
      para documentarlas, explorarlas y protegerlas.
    </p>
  </section>


  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
       FEATURE — fondo sky, texto izq + imagen der
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section id="descubrir" style="
    background:#cceae6;
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
    min-height:600px;
  ">
    <div style="
      display:flex; flex-direction:column; justify-content:center;
      padding: 5rem 4rem;
    ">
      <h3 class="reveal" style="
        font-family:'Archivo Black',sans-serif;
        font-size:clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
        color:#091d2b; margin:0 0 1.5rem; line-height:1.1;
        text-transform:uppercase;
      ">
        Cascadas<br/>de Todos<br/>Los Tiempos
      </h3>
      <p class="reveal" style="
        font-size:clamp(0.95rem, 1.4vw, 1.15rem);
        color:#091d2b; line-height:1.65; font-weight:300;
        max-width:380px; margin:0 0 2rem;
      ">
        Descubre cascadas accesibles para familias, senderos técnicos de alta
        montaña y rincones ocultos en la Patagonia. Todos los niveles,
        todas las regiones.
      </p>
      <a href="/cascadas" style="
        display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:0.5rem;
        color:#091d2b; text-decoration:none; font-size:0.85rem;
        font-weight:600; letter-spacing:0.12em; text-transform:uppercase;
        border-bottom:2px solid #091d2b; padding-bottom:0.25rem;
        width:fit-content;
      ">
        Explorar cascadas →
      </a>
    </div>
    <div style="
      background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1523906834658-6e24ef2386f9?w=900&q=80');
      background-size:cover; background-position:center;
      min-height:400px;
    "></div>
  </section>


  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
       CASCADAS GRID — fondo oscuro + cards
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section id="cascadas" style="
    background:#091d2b;
    padding: 7rem 2.5rem;
  ">
    <div style="
      display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:flex-end;
      margin-bottom:3.5rem;
    ">
      <h2 style="
        font-family:'Archivo Black',sans-serif;
        font-size:clamp(3rem, 8vw, 9rem);
        color:#f4efe6; margin:0; line-height:0.9;
        text-transform:uppercase;
      ">CASCADAS<br/>DESTACADAS</h2>
      <div style="display:flex; gap:0.75rem;">
        <button style="
          width:48px; height:48px; border-radius:50%;
          border:1.5px solid rgba(244,239,230,0.35);
          background:transparent; color:#f4efe6;
          cursor:pointer; font-size:1rem; display:flex;
          align-items:center; justify-content:center;
        ">←</button>
        <button style="
          width:48px; height:48px; border-radius:50%;
          border:1.5px solid rgba(244,239,230,0.35);
          background:#f4efe6; color:#091d2b;
          cursor:pointer; font-size:1rem; display:flex;
          align-items:center; justify-content:center;
        ">→</button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div style="
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap:1.25rem;
    ">
      {[
        { nombre: 'Salto del Laja', region: 'Araucanía', info: 'Biobío · 35 m', badge: '#00e5d4', img: 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1441974231531-c6227db76b6e?w=600&q=80', slug: 'salto-del-laja' },
        { nombre: 'Cascada de los Cántaros', region: 'Los Lagos', info: 'Llanquihue · 50 m', badge: '#b8e8e4', img: 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1518709268805-4e9042af9f23?w=600&q=80', slug: 'cascada-de-los-cantaros' },
        { nombre: 'Salto Río Ibáñez', region: 'Aysén', info: 'General Carrera · 80 m', badge: '#cceae6', img: 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1501854140801-50d01698950b?w=600&q=80', slug: 'salto-rio-ibanez' },
      ].map(c => (
        <a href={`/cascadas/${c.slug}`} class="cascade-card" style="display:block; text-decoration:none; cursor:pointer;">
          <div style={`
            height:340px;
            background-image:url('${c.img}');
            background-size:cover; background-position:center;
            border-radius:4px; margin-bottom:1.25rem;
            position:relative; overflow:hidden;
          `}>
            <span style={`
              position:absolute; top:1rem; left:1rem;
              background:${c.badge}; color:#091d2b;
              font-size:0.72rem; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:0.1em;
              text-transform:uppercase; padding:0.3rem 0.75rem; border-radius:999px;
            `}>{c.region}</span>
          </div>
          <h3 style="
            font-family:'Archivo Black',sans-serif;
            font-size:1.6rem; color:#f4efe6; margin:0 0 0.4rem;
            text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:-0.01em;
          ">{c.nombre}</h3>
          <p style="color:rgba(244,239,230,0.55); font-size:0.9rem; margin:0; font-weight:300;">{c.info}</p>
        </a>
      ))}
    </div>

    <div style="margin-top:4rem; text-align:center;">
      <a href="/cascadas" style="
        display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:0.75rem;
        color:#091d2b; background:#00e5d4; text-decoration:none;
        font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:0.12em;
        text-transform:uppercase; padding:1rem 2.5rem; border-radius:999px;
      ">
        Ver todas las cascadas →
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
       REGIONES — fondo crema + grid de regiones
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section id="regiones" style="
    background:#f4efe6;
    padding: 7rem 2.5rem;
  ">
    <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:5rem; align-items:start;">
      <div>
        <h2 class="reveal" style="
          font-family:'Archivo Black',sans-serif;
          font-size:clamp(3rem, 6vw, 6rem);
          color:#091d2b; margin:0; line-height:0.92;
          text-transform:uppercase;
        ">
          EXPLORA<br/>POR<br/>REGIÓN
        </h2>
      </div>
      <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column; justify-content:center; padding-top:0.5rem;">
        {[
          { name: 'Atacama & Coquimbo', count: '12', slug: 'atacama-coquimbo' },
          { name: 'Araucanía', count: '48', slug: 'araucania' },
          { name: 'Los Lagos & Los Ríos', count: '95', slug: 'los-lagos' },
          { name: 'Aysén', count: '73', slug: 'aysen' },
          { name: 'Magallanes', count: '38', slug: 'magallanes' },
        ].map(r => (
          <a href={`/region/${r.slug}`} style="
            display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between;
            padding:1.25rem 0; border-top:1px solid rgba(9,29,43,0.15);
            text-decoration:none; color:#091d2b;
            transition: padding-left 0.2s;
          " onmouseenter="this.style.paddingLeft='1rem'" onmouseleave="this.style.paddingLeft='0'">
            <span style="font-size:clamp(1rem, 1.8vw, 1.3rem); font-weight:500;">{r.name}</span>
            <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
              <span style="font-family:'Archivo Black',sans-serif; font-size:1.2rem; color:#00b4a0;">{r.count}</span>
              <span style="font-size:1rem; opacity:0.4;">→</span>
            </div>
          </a>
        ))}
        <div style="height:1px; background:rgba(9,29,43,0.15);"></div>
        <a href="/region" style="
          display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:0.5rem;
          color:#00b4a0; text-decoration:none; font-size:0.78rem;
          font-weight:600; letter-spacing:0.12em; text-transform:uppercase;
          margin-top:1.5rem;
        ">Ver todas las regiones →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
